    "Beyond these, OpenAssistant and OpenHermes are instruction-following datasets centered around human-AI dialogue, covering tasks like summarization, explanation, and clarification in open-ended formats.",
    "UltraChat is a high-quality, multi-turn conversational dataset designed to probe the generalization and dialogue coherence of LLMs.These tasks collectively evaluate DRaFT-Q's ability to scale across task forms (multiple-choice, freeform, chain-of-thought), modality types (textual, numerical), and alignment styles (supervised answers vs. conversational reward signals).",
    "The combination of dynamic rank reallocation and token-level reward modulation is put to test across these benchmarks to validate the method's generality and stability under realistic resource constraints.",
    "ModelsWe primarily use Falcon-RW-1B and TinyLLaMA-1.1B as our base models for all core evaluations.",
    "These 1.1-1.3B parameter decoder-only transformers strike a balance between scale and memory efficiency, making them suitable for low-resource fine-tuning on a single 16GB NVIDIA T4 GPU."
